name: Star Base #1 - Planet 444
description: It's a pixel sprite 120x120 upscale to 1200x1200 of star base from Planet 444. It's a fictional planet, that inspired from Mars. It's dry, and hot during day, but at night it's cold. Human can't endure the weather, and used drone to examine this planet. At the moment, human can live only inside the base.
